# -*- org -*-

- 0.2.0 (general-dev) :: Currently in development branch(es).

  - Implement the DRAFT file property to suppress publishing
    individual pages/posts.
  - Mindfully handle posts and pages whose publication date is after
    the current time when building the site, governed by the
    `:postdate-policy` argument to the top-level `defblog` macro.
  - Simplifying internal APIs by pushing parameters into the site
    property list.
  - Macro for clearer access to property lists.
  - Squashed tabs in the [[./README.md][README.md]] file.

- 0.1.0 :: Initial numbered release.
